OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F331A1782301689
OL,3,C'Watershed' as first grooming gangs
OL,4,Cinquiry locations named
OL,6,FLondon, Bradford and Keighley and
OL,7,FOldham will be the first places to be
OL,8,Finvestigated by the national grooming
OL,9,Fgangs inquiry, it has been announced.
OL,11,FThe #65 million probe will investigate
OL,12,Fhow gangs who sexually exploited
OL,13,Fchildren operated and how police,
OL,14,Fcouncils, health services, social care
OL,15,Fservices and schools responded.
OL,17,FOne MP hailed the news as a "watershed
OL,18,Fmoment".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
