FL,332,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F331A1782301689
OL,3,C'Watershed' as first grooming gangs
OL,4,Cinquiry locations named
OL,6,FThe areas named in Wednesday's
OL,7,Fannouncement will face so-called local
OL,8,Finvestigations ` where serious
OL,9,Ffailures have been identified.
OL,11,FFormer children's commissioner for
OL,12,FEngland Baroness Anne Longfield is
OL,13,Fheading up the inquiry, which has
OL,14,Flegal powers to compel witnesses to
OL,15,Fgive evidence and require
OL,16,Forganisations to hand over documents.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,332,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F331A1782301689
OL,3,C'Watershed' as first grooming gangs
OL,4,Cinquiry locations named
OL,6,FAny evidence of crimes uncovered will
OL,7,Fbe referred to Operation Beaconport,
OL,8,Fthe national police operation launched
OL,9,Flast year to review hundreds of
OL,10,Fpreviously closed investigations.
OL,12,FRobbie Moore, Conservative MP for
OL,13,FIlkley and Keighley, said: "This is a
OL,14,Fwatershed moment and marks a
OL,15,Fsignificant turning point in the
OL,16,Fpursuit of justice, truth and
OL,17,Faccountability for victims and
OL,18,Fsurvivors right across our area.
OL,20,F'Survivors deserve justice'
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,332,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F331A1782301689
OL,3,C'Watershed' as first grooming gangs
OL,4,Cinquiry locations named
OL,6,F"No-one will be able to hide."
OL,8,FHe paid tribute to survivors,
OL,9,Fincluding Fiona Goddard, who has
OL,10,Fwaived her right to anonymity to speak
OL,11,Fabout the abuse she suffered.
OL,13,FMs Goddard was groomed and repeatedly
OL,14,Fraped during her time in three
OL,15,Fchildren's homes in Bradford during
OL,16,Fthe late 2000s.
OL,18,F"Listening to their accounts of this
OL,19,Fcrime, I was confronted with horrors
OL,20,Fthat I will never forget," he said.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,332,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F331A1782301689
OL,3,C'Watershed' as first grooming gangs
OL,4,Cinquiry locations named
OL,6,F"I made a promise to them then that I
OL,7,Fwould do everything in my power to
OL,8,Fensure their voices were heard and the
OL,9,Ftruth would come out."
OL,11,FHe added: "Whilst no inquiry can undo
OL,12,Fthe pain and suffering they have
OL,13,Fendured, it can help ensure the truth
OL,14,Fis uncovered and that those who were
OL,15,Ffailed finally receive the answers
OL,16,Fthey have spent years fighting for."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
