FL,332,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F331A1782301689
OL,3,C'Watershed' as first grooming gangs
OL,4,Cinquiry locations named
OL,6,FShadow safeguarding minister Alicia
OL,7,FKearns added: "After years of fighting
OL,8,Fto be heard, grooming gang survivors
OL,9,Fhave secured a major breakthrough with
OL,10,Fthe announcement of the first local
OL,11,Finquiries... anyone found to have
OL,12,Ffailed children must be named, held
OL,13,Faccountable, and face consequences.
OL,15,F"Survivors deserve justice. The
OL,16,Fcountry deserves the truth."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/6
